trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleEngine"></xref> class with a <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> to evaluate and a rule type to create a new instance of <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation.%23ctor%2A> to use for rule expression validation.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleEngine"> </xref> klassen med en <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> att utvärdera och skapa en ny instans av en regeltyp <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation.%23ctor%2A> för regeln uttryck validering.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the <xref:System.Type> of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.Rule"></xref> used to create a new instance of <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation.%23ctor%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref:System.Type>av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.Rule"> </xref> används för att skapa en ny instans av <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation.%23ctor%2A>.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleEngine"></xref> class with a <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> to evaluate using <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleEngine"> </xref> klassen med en <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> att utvärdera med <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Specifies the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation"></xref> used to validate rule expressions.
trans-unit.target: Anger den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleValidation"> </xref> används för att verifiera Regeluttryck.
Kör den aktuella objekt med hjälp av <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleExecution.%23ctor%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The current object to be executed.

Executes the current <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"></xref> against the object instance (which, in this case, is likely an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref>).
trans-unit.target: Kör aktuellt <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.Rules.RuleSet"> </xref> mot objektinstansen (som i det här fallet är förmodligen en <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref>).

trans-unit.source: The current object to be executed.
